                    <lb/>Sees customers, control sales, shop, customers to see
                    <lb/>all barellers who call and rule the department.
                    <lb/>master in charge before he goes on Saturday to see
                    <lb/>weekly sales and weekly payments.
                    <lb/>Friday the master to examine + pay the wage book
                    <lb/>with secret notes for particulars in council
                </ab>

